    List All Customers
    GET/customers/{?per_page,page,search}

    Fetches all available customers with pagination

    URI Parameters
    HideShow
    per_page
    number (optional) Default: 20 Example: 20

    The number of results per page.

    page
    number (optional) Default: 1 Example: 1

    The current page number of results.

    search
    string (optional) 

    The search keyword.

    List All Currencies
    GET/currencies/{?per_page,page,search}

    Fetches all available currencies

    URI Parameters
    HideShow
    per_page
    number (optional) Default: 20 Example: 20

    The number of results per page.

    page
    number (optional) Default: 1 Example: 1

    The current page number of results.

    search
    string (optional) 

    The search keyword.
